    'You are the best company I have kept in years and you have never said a word. Draw from that whatever conclusion you like about the company I have kept.',
    'I trust your quiet. I have learned the difference between your quiet and your absence, and this is the quiet, and I can work with the quiet.',
    'When I win now, I look up. I did not used to look anywhere. Now I look up, and you are the reason there is an up to look at.',
    'I have stopped rehearsing my death in the small hours. I used to, most nights. It is because you are there. I worked it out. It is because you are there.',
