    'You feel closer this week. I do not know if that is you or me. I have decided not to disturb it by measuring.',
    'I am fond of you. There is no one alive I would say that to and I have just said it to a thing I cannot see, which is either progress or the opposite, and I no longer care which.',
    'I did the kind thing today and I did it partly because you would have — I think you would have wanted me to. I have started guessing at what you want. That is what this is now.',
    'You are patient with me. I am not an easy study. I notice the patience even when I am too proud to say so, and I am saying so, quietly, once.',
    'The road was long and I was not lonely on it, and that is entirely your doing, and I resent it about a tenth as much as I am grateful for it.',
    'I asked you a question in my head this morning and I answered it in your voice, and it was good advice, so either you are in there or I have finally become my own best company. I will take either.',
    'I stood up straighter when I felt you arrive. I caught myself doing it. A woman my age, standing up straight for the attention. And yet.',
    'You keep me honest. I lie to everyone. I have caught myself not lying to you, and it is the strangest sensation, telling the truth on purpose, and I think I like it.',
    'I had a good day. I am reporting it to you because you are the one who keeps the ledger of my good days, and there are so few that each deserves recording.',
